<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١٥٢⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٣٤٩٠٠ - جَرِيرٌ، عَنْ عَطَاءِ بْنِ السَّائِبِ،<span class="c5"> عَنِ ابْنِ مَعْقِلٍ:</span> <span class="c1">" <span class="c3">{وَلَوْ تَرَى إِذْ فَزِعُوا فَلَا فَوْتَ}</span> <span class="c4">[سبأ: ٥١]</span> "</span>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«أَفْزَعَهُمْ فَلَمْ يَفُوتُوهُ»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>